<div id="found-lower" class="white-popup mfp-hide tp-popup">
    <div class="tp-popup__body tp-popup__body--lower">
        <div class="t-center">
            <div class="h3 h3-h2-mob c-main">Find a similar trailer with a lower price?</div>
            <div class="h4 margin-10t br-sm">Let us know where and we will get back to you<br>
                in 1 business day.</div>
        </div>
        <form action="#" class="tp-form margin-30t" id="found-lower-cf">
            <div class="tp-form-control">
                <input type="text" name="url" placeholder="Website with lower price" required="required">
            </div>
            <div class="t-center h4 margin-30t margin-20b">Your Contact Details</div>
            <div class="tp-form-double">
                <div class="tp-form-control">
                    <input type="text" name="first_name" minlength="3" placeholder="First Name*" required="required">
                </div>
                <div class="tp-form-control">
                    <input type="text" name="last_name" minlength="3" placeholder="Last Name*" required="required">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="tp-form-control">
                <input type="email" name="email" pattern="^([a-zA-Z0-9_\-\.]+)@((\[[0-9]{1,3}\.[0-9]{1,3}\.[0-9]{1,3}\.)|(([a-zA-Z0-9\-]+\.)+))([a-zA-Z]{2,4}|[0-9]{1,3})(\]?)$" placeholder="Email*" required="required">
            </div>
            <div class="tp-form-double">
                <div class="tp-form-control">
                    <input type="tel" name="phone" placeholder="Phone*" required="required">
                </div>
                <div class="tp-form-control">
                    <input type="number" name="zip" min="0" placeholder="Zip Code">
                </div>
            </div>

            <input type="hidden" name="trailer" value="4RADG1628LN111914"/>

            <div class="tp-form-msg t-center">
                <div class="tp-form-msg__text tp-form-msg__text--success margin-30t">Form successfully submitted</div>
                <div class="tp-form-msg__text tp-form-msg__text--error margin-30t"></div>
            </div>

            <div class="margin-15t">
                <button type="submit" class="tp-btn tp-btn--red tp-btn--full">
                    <span>Submit</span>
                    <div class="tp-btn__loader"></div>
                </button>
            </div>
        </form>
        <div class="t-center fz14 margin-30t">
            Trailer makes and models vary by region. For set specifications and measurements, quality of the trailer build may vary by manufacturer and regional price differences. We will try our best to match the regular pricing given comparable specifications and measurements (sale, clearance & closeout pricing not applicable in the same market). Upon submission of this form, our team will review the content and reach back out to you within 1 business day. We reserve the right to decline any price match request under our discretion. Not responsible for pricing or typographical errors.
        </div>
    </div>
</div>